Mary Anne TAGOE, aka Mary Anne Roberts, petitioner,
v.
DISTRICT OF COLUMBIA DEPARTMENT OF EMPLOYMENT SERVICES, et al. No. 13-6892. Supreme Court of the United States Feb. 24, 2014.

Former decision, 134 S.Ct. 983.

Motion of petitioner for reconsideration of order denying leave to proceed in forma pauperis denied.
